<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <style>
      body { font-family: sans-serif; color: #333; max-width: 480px; margin: 40px auto; }
      .code { font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 0.3em;
              color: #1a56db; background: #f0f4ff; padding: 16px 24px;
              border-radius: 8px; display: inline-block; margin: 16px 0; }
      .footer { font-size: 0.85rem; color: #888; margin-top: 24px; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h2>Your verification code</h2>
    <p>Use the code below to verify your identity. It expires in <strong><%= @expires_in %></strong>.</p>
    <div class="code"><%= @code %></div>
    <p>If you didn't request this, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
    <p class="footer">Finance Tracker — do not reply to this email.</p>
  </body>
</html>
